---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import { getLangFromUrl, useTranslations, getNavLink } from '../utils/i18n';

const lang = getLangFromUrl(Astro.url);
const t = useTranslations(lang);
---

<Layout title={`${t('nav.faq')} | ${t('site.title')}`} description={t('meta.faq.description')}>
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header text-center mb-4">
        <h1>Frequently Asked Questions</h1>
        <p class="text-large">Find answers to common questions about Espai.ai</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="faq-container">
        <div class="faq-category">
          <h2>General Questions</h2>
          
          <div class="faq-item">
            <button class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
              <span>What is Espai.ai?</span>
              <span class="faq-icon">+</span>
            </button>
            <div class="faq-answer">
              <p>Espai.ai is an AI platform that automatically records all events and actions in your system. We use our AI model to analyze these processes, create timelines, detect repetitive processes and bottlenecks, identifying which variables are involved in each process.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="faq-item">
            <button class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
              <span>How does the recording system work?</span>
              <span class="faq-icon">+</span>
            </button>
            <div class="faq-answer">
              <p>Our software installs on your systems and automatically begins recording all events and actions. You don't need to configure anything. The AI analyzes this information securely to create personalized automations.</p>
              <p><strong>Privacy guaranteed:</strong> Your data remains completely private as it will not be seen by any person nor used to train our models. If we want to use your data, we will contact you to reach a prior agreement.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="faq-item">
            <button class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
              <span>What kind of insights can I get?</span>
              <span class="faq-icon">+</span>
            </button>
            <div class="faq-answer">
              <p>You get valuable insights about where your employees spend their time, which processes are repetitive, where bottlenecks are, and which variables affect each process. This information allows you to make decisions to improve performance.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="faq-category">
          <h2>Pricing and Business Model</h2>
          
          <div class="faq-item">
            <button class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
              <span>How does per-device pricing work?</span>
              <span class="faq-icon">+</span>
            </button>
            <div class="faq-answer">
              <p>Unlike other providers who charge per automation, we charge per device. This makes our pricing super competitive. You can create as many automations as you want without additional cost.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="faq-item">
            <button class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
              <span>Is it true that I don't pay until I save time?</span>
              <span class="faq-icon">+</span>
            </button>
            <div class="faq-answer">
              <p>Correct. You don't pay until you start saving your employees' time. Until automations start working and generating real, measurable savings, you pay nothing.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="faq-item">
            <button class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
              <span>How do you measure time savings?</span>
              <span class="faq-icon">+</span>
            </button>
            <div class="faq-answer">
              <p>Our system automatically measures the time saved with each automation. We compare the time manual processes took with automated time, providing clear and transparent metrics.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="faq-category">
          <h2>Implementation and Support</h2>
          
          <div class="faq-item">
            <button class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
              <span>What does installation include?</span>
              <span class="faq-icon">+</span>
            </button>
            <div class="faq-answer">
              <p>We handle everything: software installation on your systems, initial setup, and deployment. You don't need to do anything technical. Our team takes care of the entire implementation.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="faq-item">
            <button class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
              <span>Can I see my processes in real-time?</span>
              <span class="faq-icon">+</span>
            </button>
            <div class="faq-answer">
              <p>Yes, you can see in real-time and from mobile how all your processes are performing. Our adaptive dashboards let you not miss a single data point and supervise automations from anywhere.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="faq-item">
            <button class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
              <span>Is my data secure?</span>
              <span class="faq-icon">+</span>
            </button>
            <div class="faq-answer">
              <p>Absolutely. All data is encrypted and processed securely. We comply with GDPR and other security standards. Your business information remains completely private and protected.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="faq-category">
          <h2>Automations</h2>
          
          <div class="faq-item">
            <button class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
              <span>How are automations created?</span>
              <span class="faq-icon">+</span>
            </button>
            <div class="faq-answer">
              <p>Once our AI model has enough information, you receive detailed reports and specific automation recommendations. You can apply these recommendations under your supervision.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="faq-item">
            <button class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
              <span>Can I control what gets automated?</span>
              <span class="faq-icon">+</span>
            </button>
            <div class="faq-answer">
              <p>Of course. All automations are applied under your supervision. You decide which processes to automate and can activate or deactivate any automation at any time.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="faq-item">
            <button class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
              <span>Is there a limit on the number of automations?</span>
              <span class="faq-icon">+</span>
            </button>
            <div class="faq-answer">
              <p>No limits. Since we charge per device and not per automation, you can create as many automations as you need without additional cost. This is what makes our model super competitive.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="contact-section text-center mt-4">
        <h2>Still have questions?</h2>
        <p>Can't find the answer you're looking for? Our team is here to help.</p>
        <a href={getNavLink('contact', lang)} class="btn">Contact Support</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .faq-container {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  
  .faq-category {
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }
  
  .faq-category h2 {
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
    border-bottom: 2px solid var(--accent);
  }
  
  .faq-item {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    border-radius: 12px;
    overflow: hidden;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }
  
  .faq-item:hover {
    border-color: var(--accent);
  }
  
  .faq-question {
    width: 100%;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
    border: none;
    color: var(--space-white);
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-align: left;
    cursor: pointer;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }
  
  .faq-question:hover {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
  }
  
  .faq-icon {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 300;
    color: var(--accent);
    transition: transform 0.3s ease;
  }
  
  .faq-answer {
    padding: 0 1.5rem;
    max-height: 0;
    overflow: hidden;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }
  
  .faq-answer.active {
    padding: 1.5rem;
    max-height: 1000px;
  }
  
  .faq-item.active .faq-icon {
    transform: rotate(45deg);
  }
  
  .contact-section {
    background: radial-gradient(circle at center, rgba(6, 182, 212, 0.1) 0%, transparent 70%);
    padding: 3rem 2rem;
    border-radius: 16px;
    margin-top: 3rem;
  }
  
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .faq-question {
      padding: 1rem;
      font-size: 1rem;
    }
    
    .faq-answer.active {
      padding: 1rem;
      max-height: 1000px;
    }
  }
</style>

<script>
  function toggleFaq(button) {
    const faqItem = button.parentElement;
    const answer = faqItem.querySelector('.faq-answer');
    
    // Close all other FAQ items
    document.querySelectorAll('.faq-item').forEach(item => {
      if (item !== faqItem) {
        item.classList.remove('active');
        item.querySelector('.faq-answer').classList.remove('active');
      }
    });
    
    // Toggle current FAQ item
    faqItem.classList.toggle('active');
    answer.classList.toggle('active');
  }
  
  // Make function global
  window.toggleFaq = toggleFaq;
</script> 